Expression in If Tests
======================

Simple expression condition:
{{if @(intvalue10 > 5)}}Ten is greater than 5{{endif}}

Expression with else:
{{if @(intvalue2 > 5)}}Two > 5{{else}}Two <= 5{{endif}}

Arithmetic in condition:
{{if @(intvalue10 + intvalue2 > 10)}}Sum is big{{else}}Sum is small{{endif}}

Multiple conditions with and:
{{if @(intvalue10 > 5 and intvalue2 > 1)}}Both conditions met{{endif}}

Multiple conditions with or:
{{if @(intvalue10 < 5 or intvalue2 > 1)}}At least one condition met{{endif}}

Comparison with equality:
{{if @(intvalue10 = 10)}}Value equals 10{{endif}}

Nested parentheses:
{{if @((intvalue10 + intvalue2) * intvalue1 > 10)}}Complex condition true{{endif}}
